  Locus:
    Page: 169
    Verse: 3
Tags:
  - Forgiveness
---
A forgiving spirit is by its very nature a unifying force. It can remove
the barriers of separation between peoples and nations and weld them together
in peace and goodwill; something that legislation with the help of armies
can never accomplish.
